== ./myapp views ==
layouts/main -> packages/atlantis/tests/corpus/views_layout/Resources/Views/layouts/main.lhtml
links/_list -> packages/atlantis/tests/corpus/views_layout/Resources/Views/links/_list.lhtml
links/index -> packages/atlantis/tests/corpus/views_layout/Resources/Views/links/index.lhtml, layout=layouts/main, blocks=[title, footer], partials=[links/_list]
